Actually, though I imagine the entrance being similar to the second base in
Beast Wars, this is the abandoned Silver Wing Maximal base outside Relay
City.  Relay floats in the air above the great lakes, I imagine this being
on the ground somewhere near the shore of the lakes.  I don&#39;t think it has a
connection to the Beast Wars cartoon.  The few Silver Wings we had active
were chased out of the base by Jhaxius and they came to Atlantis.

I imagine this being sort of a mine shaft design where the floor slopes down
slowly from the entrance.  There might be a back exit tunnel that the minons
can use.  But it won&#39;t be obvious from the outside.

