described it a bit in Message #69458, and of course Tuscon left on his
mission to the black fortress from there, so you should be familiar with it
already :) Just don&#39;t forget the huge two headed dragon floating above it.
So far it has not attacked.

Since this is Kraftlos&#39; show over there, you might want to get with him as
well if you have any questions. I will help as I can :)

The Ark of course looks much like it did in the old 80&#39;s cartoon, except
that you have Autobots and Decepticons laying around inside it . . . much
like the description I gave for Quickstride&#39;s benefit. Also there is a force
field which Lord Elder or Kup can lower to let Tuscon in.

I hope this is helpful?

